"As Head Researcher, I need the database to be updated every time a questionnaire is completed, so that I view the most up-to-date responses."
label:  Deliver Next (Low Risk/High Value)
Moscow: Must

background:  the head researcher may be wanting to work in real time, this means that when a questionnaire is completed the new data is added to the tables
in the database.  This also means that unless a 'Limit' has been applied to result queries, charts and visualisations of the data should contain new 
information upon page refresh.
